## Competitive Differentiation Dimensions

- **Product**: Feature superiority, performance, reliability, integrations
- **Experience**: Onboarding ease, support quality, community, UX
- **Business model**: Pricing, deployment flexibility, free tier
- **Brand**: Mission, thought leadership, category creation, trust
- **Ecosystem**: Partner network, developer community, data network effects

